Package io.github.agroportal.ncboproxy

Class AbstractServletHandler

java.lang.Object
io.github.agroportal.ncboproxy.AbstractServletHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
ServletHandler
public abstract class AbstractServletHandler extends Object implements ServletHandler
Handles handler registrations and overrides for ServletHandler implementing classes, please use the following three private methods: registerParameterHandler, registerResponsePostProcessor, registerOutputGenerator
